author: Just Jared
title: Jamie Dornan Shaves Head - See the Photos!
text:
Jamie Dornan shaved his head!
The 34-year-old Fifty Shades Darker star was seen walking through LAX Airport on Sunday (January 29) showing off his brand new look.
We’re not entirely sure if Jamie shaved his head by his own choice, or if it is for an upcoming film role! He’s rumored to be starring in next year’s Robin Hood movie as Will Scarlet.
If you missed it, be sure to check out the super steamy date night scene from Fifty Shades Darker , which was released over the weekend (it’s NSFW!).
10+ pictures inside of Jamie Dornan showing off his new shaved head…
